{"tid":476457,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解United States 前面會加the","createTime":"2017-11-22T04:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T01:17:40.000Z","uid":61494,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d27e003fe4350cd078e92476a7bdedfa27e804af","tid":476457,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:21:26.000Z","msg":"專有名詞唔係唔駛既咩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.usa.gov/about-the-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usa.gov%2Fabout-the-us&d=0RPuTf6AeM3Pf2%2BE24Au0IS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=c5a6cdcb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.usa.gov/about-the-us</a>"},{"pid":"1484eeae820cb63d7ae5364acf1e4d20e2657635","tid":476457,"uid":14566,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"「英國」當然可以用「England」或「Great Britain」，可是更常用到的卻是「UK」。<br />\n \t「UK」，是「United Kingdom」的縮寫，好玩的是，在這種情況之下，一定要加定冠詞「the」在前面ㄡ。為什麼這麼麻煩呢？原來是因為這個「united」的「kingdom」，包含了切確的不同領土，有英格蘭、蘇格蘭、威爾斯、以及北愛爾蘭這四個部分，所以才要加定冠詞「the」。<br />\n \t <br />\n \t同理，美國一定要用「the USA」，因為是固定的那五十幾州啊。當然，這個用法，是出現在句子之中，若是寫住址的時候，當然越簡潔越好，定冠詞「the」就會被省略了。正確答案是(A)，這也是一般同學常犯的小錯誤，要小心一點喲！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n常識吧"},{"pid":"d674c57e998fd95bd15e913bbc378a83ed3a858b","tid":476457,"uid":14566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThe White House<br />\nThe Atlantic<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大把專用名詞都要加冠詞"},{"pid":"5fd7332c2bfe8df03e05b1b8eb126934a3b0cafa","tid":476457,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"The Philippines"},{"pid":"dc0ed47064c38d481131567786f192a71534b0e5","tid":476457,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"其實好似除左英文 好多歐洲語言咩noun都需要用the<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽個老師解完都唔明"},{"pid":"8f2e1ccfdc4e9ec83c00add3ec03ab2a11507a34","tid":476457,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T23:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThe White House<br />\nThe Atlantic<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大把專用名詞都要加冠詞</blockquote><br />\n點分"},{"pid":"1bb567eb0ef969a02404a2d6a48f3b5308f3ca6c","tid":476457,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cacace74ca27f401f7d93c8eee3df35318659bd6","tid":476457,"uid":19979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實好似除左英文 好多歐洲語言咩noun都需要用the<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽個老師解完都唔明</blockquote><br />\n語言呢d野邊有得解</blockquote><br />\nWhat the fuck"},{"pid":"f381bbd1cf4e91e6bb24e783a5d530dc54795ec4","tid":476457,"uid":24642,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:55:15.000Z","msg":"國家名、地名、人名等等，本身係專有名詞（Proper Noun），唔使用固定冠詞i.e. the<br />\n 例子：Egypt, Hong Kong, Mary<br />\n<br />\n但當個國家名入面 有 普通名詞，就要加the<br />\n例子：the United States (有States 呢個普通名詞）, the United Kingdom（有Kingdom 呢個字）<br />\n<br />\n仲有 群島國家例如the Philippines 都要加the<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔使特別去記點解，只係要死記個別國家名要加the<br />\nthe UK, the US, the Philippines<br />\n<br />\n有錯請糾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913cf8633d7d0889005022fac3984066e2e32d25","tid":476457,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:28:02.000Z","msg":"the 皮又點解釋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46748a2134a1271f73ac8e73409249f19de60922","tid":476457,"uid":155601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國家名、地名、人名等等，本身係專有名詞（Proper Noun），唔使用固定冠詞i.e. the<br />\n 例子：Egypt, Hong Kong, Mary<br />\n<br />\n但當個國家名入面 有 普通名詞，就要加the<br />\n例子：the United States (有States 呢個普通名詞）, the United Kingdom（有Kingdom 呢個字）<br />\n<br />\n仲有 群島國家例如the Philippines 都要加the<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔使特別去記點解，只係要死記個別國家名要加the<br />\nthe UK, the US, the Philippines<br />\n<br />\n有錯請糾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有 the Ukraine"}]}